      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the S65 high-revving naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis remains factory-stiff with no subframe fatigue, and the M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional power delivery through the rear wheels. Meticulously maintained, this unit features pristine EDC (Electronic Damper Control) hydraulics and a flawless finish with original paint depth. All critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been performed and documented. This is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance in its most refined state.",
